         <text>ECM BOMs</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2DA86255-A662-43E9-B312-936B6DC3CDBC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>PDM-related BOM Data are requested in SPEED System

PDM integration layer translates SPEED data before sending to the S/4
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-622D9CAA-8210-46A9-90B9-FFB1F9CD0D80" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>S/4 (IF &amp; IP) send the BOM data to ECA BOM with same MM ID’s and New location.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
